    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for practical transportation. The engine and transmission are in functional working order, though the car does show its age with some noticeable exterior scratches and thinning paint in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery has some minor staining and signs of wear, but the cabin remains comfortable. It is a solid choice for someone who prioritizes mechanical dependability over cosmetic perfection.",
