      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously preserved and mechanically flawless, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, affirms its status as an investment-grade acquisition. We invite you to experience a standard of excellence that transcends the ordinary.",
      "price": 48500.0,
